{"tid":1382437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方短片顯示警棍拔掉繩索後索帶需用手才能推到前端","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:39.000Z","uid":90306,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11d2cacb4633cc4f0812d65adcbe1f9fea764d48","tid":1382437,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即係特登拉上前頭到扑頭啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471213-20190729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471213-20190729.htm&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiibrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=36606053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471213-20190729.htm&h=3c1fea70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471213-20190729.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方在社交媒體發佈短片，澄清周六在元朗衝突中，有警員被拍攝到警棍上疑似套上金屬環，實際上是膠索帶。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科警司劉肇邦在短片說，經了解，膠索帶用來固定警棍尾部繩索，混亂期間，若繩索鬆脫，索帶就會滑到警棍前端，不存在警員故意加裝攻擊性工具。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">短片所見，警員示範拔掉繩索後，索帶並沒有在警棍上滑動，需要用手才能將索帶推到警棍前端，多次揮動警棍時，索帶亦沒有移位。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外劉肇邦又說，警方在昨日上環、西環一帶的示威中，檢獲多件武器，有示威者手持約兩米長的長矛與警員對峙，亦有警員遭「丫叉」射中，批評示威者對警員的襲擊有針對性，亦不顧後果。"},{"pid":"28ecfb4a0d7e1d4a8f8a15b2a1b5aaa58272b3cf","tid":1382437,"uid":90306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"就算索帶都係硬膠尖角 都係會爆頭"},{"pid":"dff8061a544e1499740829334baa10c65e0866d0","tid":1382437,"uid":90306,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"無人炒車呀<br />\n索帶根本就唔應該係個棍頭度"},{"pid":"b22257b8790cf0f017ec42433576ff849606b18f","tid":1382437,"uid":90306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:11:03.000Z","msg":"自推十下<br />\n1"},{"pid":"3e78640c72d4a49faf07e57ba886617431465121","tid":1382437,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201